Introduction¶

In this project we will be analizing data associated with a list of TMDb movies. we are interested in finding trends amoung the movies in order to fill in the gaps and help us get to a conclusion that would help us get an answer for our questions.

Question(s) for Analysis¶

  • Q: Which genres are most popular from year to year?
  • Q: What kinds of properties are associated with movies that have high Profits?
  • Q: Does higher budget movies means higher profits?
  • Q: Which year has the most popular movies?
  • Q: Who is the best director of high quality movies?

Data Cleaning¶

we will clean our data in just three simple steps

  1. Filter drop the columns of data that we are not going to use

  1. Drop Nulls Drop any rows in both datasets that contain missing values.

  2. Dedupe Drop any duplicate rows in both datasets.

  1. Drop useless Columns
